headline.print_headline: Serena Beats Sharapova to Reach Ninth Miami Final
headline.main: Serena Beats Sharapova to Reach Ninth Miami Final

lead_paragraph: World number one Serena Williams continued her decade-long domination over Maria Sharapova with a clinical 6-4 6-3 win on Thursday to reach her ninth Sony Open final.
